Create a configuration/installation script with automatic :
- Database and framework settings generation
For all framework / site files:
- CHMOD 505 for all directories
- CHMOD 404 for all files (will make all files read-only)
For all upload/working directories:
- CHMOD 604 for files
- CHMOD 705 for directories
For all .htaccess files:
- CHMOD 404

In root htaccess:
- disallow hotlinking of static resources files

For database:
- allow prefix for table

For security:
- create files signature check script
- read http://phpsec.org/projects/guide/